reviewText: Good period piece. Probably transferred from the best available film elements, but just a tiny bit washed out. Certainly well worth the money and fun to watch.
Good B flick for the period.

Atmospheric and tense action keeps the viewer enthralled throughout. Characters with hidden motives provide great entertainment and leave you thoroughly satisfied with their highlt crafted performances. A low budget maybe, but a high quality movie gem.
A very good story line. And well produced for the time it was made. Each time I watch it I will pick up something I missed before.
